data.value: Green Dragon Game Downloader, is a program that downloads free games. Currently this uses the games from "Game Downloader" so I have also decided to make it look like "Game Downloader" too. It's kind of appropriate isn't it? The reason for not making a database of games for my client is that I feel like I shouldn't need to go jumping around searching for free games.
